    <descript>
      <abstract>This gridded land cover map was created by unsupervised classification of a Landsat 5 Thematic Mapper image (Chatfield and Graham, 1992).  The classification accuracy was improved by stitching a 1987 SPOT image into known problem areas in the classified Landsat image.  The 1987 SPOT image was classified through a supervised classification approach. The overall accuracy of the final image was assessed at 82%.

Land cover legend
0 No data
1 Water 
2 Urban
4 Open/Grasses
5 Ag. Fileds/Bare Ground
6 Hardwoods
7 Hardwood-Pine Mix
8 Pine Plantations


